El Alami Group bụ otu nke Abdelaziz El Alami Hassani guzobere (nke nwere isi na Tangier).
Taa, Abdelhouahed El Alami (onye ọka iwu site na ọrụ) na CEO Mourad El Bied na-eduzi otu ahụ
Otu ahụ lekwasịrị anya na ụlọ ọrụ iwu ụlọ.
Mgbe afọ abụọ nke stagnation gasịrị na 2006/2007, ìgwè ahụ ji nwayọọ nwayọọ na-ahapụ azụmahịa ya (ire Jacob Delafon, na-ahapụ Afric Industry,) iji malite na ụlọ ọrụ na hoteliers.
